    "created_at": "2025-06-04T12:46:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-06-04T12:46:18Z",
    "body": "I got the same situation while I was trying to run [fastfetch](https://github.com/fastfetch-cli/fastfetch) upon shell opening, and I finally fixxed it by using `clink set clink.autostart`, see the [clink document](https://chrisant996.github.io/clink/clink.html#clink_autostart) for more details.\nIn fact it is a way to run something after clink was injected, and I found that starship coulden't be loaded correctly while I was trying to run anything before clink was injected by seting the registry key.",
